Package: SeaSondeR
Title: Tools for Processing SeaSonde HF-Radar Data
Version: 0.2.3.9002
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan Luis", "Herrera Cortijo", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4206-2459"))
Description: A comprehensive set of tools for processing and analyzing data 
    from the SeaSonde High-Frequency Radar (HF-Radar) instrument. This package is intended to 
    facilitate the handling of raw and processed data, including spectral matrices, calibration, 
    and metadata management.
